the first thing I otice abot this data set is taht not all countries ar included. I also notice that country is contained within brackets rather than contained within its own data field. This would allow separation and identification of country of origin to be easier. a source would also be beneficial, to allow comparision of discrepancies between similar datasets. Also, brewer sub categorie could ba added to allow brand sun categories to be distinguished.

Alos there is no definition of quantities per measurement for percent, calories and carbohydrates. Although these seem to be univerrsal it makes it difficult to assess whether any mean, max or min values would be trustworthy, for this reason.

I think this probably shown in a data frame already. I will test this by doing the following:
